==English==
===Proper noun===
'''[[World]] [[War]] [[I]]'''

#The war from 1914 to 1918 between the Entente Powers of the British Empire, United States, Russia, Italy and other allied nations, against the Central Powers represented by Germany, Austria-Hungary, the Ottoman Empire, and Bulgaria.

====Synonyms====
*the [[First World War]]
*the [[Great War]]
*the war to end all wars

